text.0:
A Facebook post claiming that a deer "became riddled with tumours from eating plants sprayed with Monsanto’s Roundup" herbicide is :cross_mark: FALSE.

:magnifying_glass_tilted_right: The deer had fibromas which are caused by the well-known papillomavirus: https://t.co/irn3WvVQ38
text.1:
A tweet with a video claiming to show recent violence in Zanzibar following a disputed election is :cross_mark: FALSE.

:magnifying_glass_tilted_right: The clip has been used to make false claims in different countries and was debunked earlier this year in relation to a claim from Nigeria: https://t.co/ARi9cXAjkx
text.2:
A Facebook post claiming presidential aspirant Robert Kyagulanyi, also known as Bobi Wine, has vowed to expel citizens of China and India currently living in Uganda is :cross_mark: FALSE.

:magnifying_glass_tilted_right: The claim misrepresents an interview he gave on television: https://t.co/PTQGBZrDup
text.3:
:police_car_light: HOAX: A Facebook page with a post advertising 9,400 casual jobs at Coca-Cola in Kenya is fake.

:warning_selector: The page is not owned or managed by the company, and has changed its name seven times: https://t.co/Gs6fdRz09Y
text.4:
A Facebook post with an image announcing a nationwide power outage on the second day of the 2020 presidential nominations in Uganda is :cross_mark: FALSE.

:high_voltage: Power distributor Umeme Limited has urged the public to disregard the announcement: https://t.co/kP13o9I0QV
text.5:
A Facebook post with a video showing motorbikes and vehicles crisscrossing a wide and busy intersection and claiming this is in Kisii, Kenya, is :cross_mark: FALSE.

:motor_scooter: The video is of traffic at a busy intersection in Ho Chi Minh City in Vietnam: https://t.co/cND3OB9qus
text.6:
:police_car_light: HOAX: A Facebook post promoting a youth consultative meeting on the Building Bridges Initiative (BBI) to be hosted by Kenya’s deputy president, William Ruto, is fake.

:magnifying_glass_tilted_right: Mr Ruto’s communications director has dismissed the post: https://t.co/CdZdBpuU18
